      "id": "RQ-0006",
      "status": "done",
      "title": "Implement exponential webhook retry backoff with jitter and cap",
      "description": "Audit notes `webhook/worker/delivery.rs::retry_delay` uses linear backoff (`base × retry_number`), which can hammer endpoints during outages. Switch to exponential backoff with jitter and a maximum cap, preserving existing timeout/redaction behavior. Outcome: retry storm risk is reduced under prolonged failures.\n\nValidation: `retry_delay` is `Duration::from_millis(base.as_millis().saturating_mul(retry_number as u128).min(...))` — strictly linear in `retry_number` with no jitter or exponential term.",
