      "status": "done",
      "title": "Make runner stream decoding UTF-8 safe across fixed read chunks",
      "description": "Historical issue: `String::from_utf8_lossy` on each fixed read could split UTF-8 sequences and emit U+FFFD at chunk boundaries. Resolution: `Utf8ChunkDecoder` in `crates/ralph/src/runner/execution/stream_reader.rs` buffers trailing incomplete UTF-8 across reads for both `spawn_reader` and `spawn_json_reader`; lossy decoding applies only to invalid bytes or an incomplete tail at EOF.",
